>> time required: 30 minutes
>> tags: dinner
>> num_cooks: 1.5

Soak @bulgur wheat{3/4%cup} in warm water for ~{30 minutes}.

Mix @onion{1/4}, @mint{0.4%oz}, @ground beef{1%lb}, @egg{1} and @olive oil{3%tbsp}.

Season with @ras el hanout{2%tbsp}, @salt{1/2%tsp} and @pepper{1/2%tsp}.

Drain @bulgur wheat{} and mix with the remaining ingredients.

Pre-heat oven to 375F.

Grease the #baking sheet{} with @olive oil{} and spread the mix uniformly.

Bake for ~{30 minutes}.
